57 class MatlabFileReader : private Uncopyable {
58  public:
59  ~MatlabFileReader() { Close(); }
60  explicit MatlabFileReader()
61  : mat_fp_(nullptr) {}
62  explicit MatlabFileReader(const std::string& file_name)
63  : mat_fp_(nullptr) {
64  if (!Open(file_name)) {
65  ROS_ERROR("MatlabFileReader: could not load file %s.",
66  file_name.c_str());
67  }
68  }
69 
70  // Open and close a file. Open returns bool upon success.
71  bool Open(const std::string& file_name);
72  void Close() {
73  if (IsOpen()) Mat_Close(mat_fp_);
74  }
75 
76  // Is this reader open?
77  bool IsOpen() { return mat_fp_; }
78 
79  // Read string. Returns bool indicating success.
80  bool ReadString(const std::string& field_name, std::string* value);
81 
82  // Read scalar. Returns bool indicating success.
83  bool ReadScalar(const std::string& field_name, double* value);
84  bool ReadScalar(const std::string& field_name, size_t* value);
85 
86  // Read vector. Returns bool indicating success.
87  bool ReadVector(const std::string& field_name, std::vector<double>* values);
88  bool ReadVector(const std::string& field_name, std::vector<size_t>* values);
89 
90  private:
91  mat_t* mat_fp_;
92 }; //\class MatlabFileReader
